<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Air Quality Resources | Your Project Name</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/resources.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <a href="home" class="home-button">Home</a>
        <h1>Air Quality Resources</h1>
        <p>Trusted data sources and valuable information about air pollution</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Our Primary Data Sources</h2>
        <p>
          We rely on these authoritative platforms for accurate, real-time air
          quality information and weather forecast.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="landscape-card">
        <div class="category-header">
          <h3>Core Data Providers</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="landscape-body" style="justify-content: space-between">
          <div class="resource-item" style="text-align: left; max-width: 45%">
            <div class="resource-title">World Air Quality Index (WAQI)</div>
            <div class="resource-description">
              Comprehensive global air quality platform providing real-time
              monitoring and forecast data.
            </div>
            <a href="https://waqi.info" class="resource-link" target="_blank"
              >Visit WAQI</a
            >
          </div>

          <div class="resource-item" style="text-align: right; max-width: 45%">
            <div class="resource-title">OpenWeather</div>
            <div class="resource-description">
              Global weather data API offering current conditions
              of weather and forecast data.
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://openweathermap.org/"
              class="resource-link"
              target="_blank"
              >Visit OpenWeather</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="landscape-card">
        <div class="category-header">
          <h3>Other Research & Education Sources</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="three-column-body">
          <div class="column">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">WHO Air Quality</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                Global air pollution exposure data from the World Health
                Organization.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.who.int/data/gho/data/themes/air-pollution"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Access Data</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="column">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">State of Global Air</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                Annual reports on air quality trends and health impacts
                worldwide.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.stateofglobalair.org"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >View Reports</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="column">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">EPA AirNow</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                U.S. government's air quality resource center with educational
                materials.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.airnow.gov"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Visit Site</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="intro">
        <h2>Understanding Air Quality Data</h2>
        <p>
          Learn how to interpret air quality information and protect your
          health.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-categories">
        <div class="category">
          <div class="category-header">
            <h3>AQI Guides</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="category-body">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Air Quality Index Basics</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                EPA's guide to understanding the Air Quality Index and health
                implications.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.airnow.gov/aqi/aqi-basics/"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Read Guide</a
              >
            </div>

            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Global AQI Standards</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                How different countries calculate and report air quality
                indices.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://waqi.info/#/faq"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Learn Differences</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="category">
          <div class="category-header">
            <h3>Health Information</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="category-body">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Health Effects of Pollution</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                Comprehensive guide to health impacts from the American Lung
                Association.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.lung.org/clean-air/outdoors/health-impacts"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Read Guide</a
              >
            </div>

            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Protection Strategies</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                CDC recommendations for reducing exposure to air pollution.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.cdc.gov/air/pollution_faq.htm"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >View Recommendations</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="category">
          <div class="category-header">
            <h3>Technical Resources</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="category-body">
            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Air Quality APIs</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                Developer resources for accessing air quality data
                programmatically.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://docs.openaq.org"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >OpenAQ API Docs</a
              >
            </div>

            <div class="resource-item">
              <div class="resource-title">Monitoring Technology</div>
              <div class="resource-description">
                Guide to how air quality is measured and monitored.
              </div>
              <a
                href="https://www.epa.gov/air-sensor-toolbox/how-air-quality-measured"
                class="resource-link"
                target="_blank"
                >Learn Monitoring</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <p>Â© 2025 AirVista | Air Quality Index Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
          We gratefully acknowledge all data providers who make this work
          possible.
        </p>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="/about" class="footer-link">About Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
